content.rendered:
Directed by Gopichand Malineni.

Written by Gopichand Malineni. Abburi Ravi. Mayank Jain.

Cast Sai Dharam Tej(Siddharth ‘Siddu’ Reddy (as Sai Dharam Teja)). Rakul Preet Singh(Sitara). Jagapathi Babu(Mahendra Reddy) .Adarsh. Sonia Agarwal(Mahendra Reddy’s wife). Mohammad Ali(Horseman Babu / Peter Hens (as Ali)).Apoorva. Raghu Babu(Dharmendra Reddy’s PA). Anasuya Bharadwaj(Item number). Master Charith(Young Siddu).Captain Chowdary. Rana Daggubati(Narrator).Divya.Ashish Gandhi.Sammeta Gandhi.Venu Gopal.Hariharan.Raghu Kumar Karumanchi. Kaveri(Lakshmi (as Kalyani)).Kavitha. Mukhtar Khan(KR). Vennela Kishore(Padma).Krishnamurthy.Vijay Kumar.Madhavi.Kola Mahesh.Maheshwari. Gopichand Malineni(Biker (Guest Role)).Mallikarjun.Mangili. Duvvasi Mohan(Constable).Padmini.Kvv Panthulu.Pravalika.Priya. Mamilla Shailaja Priya(Sitara’s Mother). Priyadarshi Pulikonda((as Priyadarshi)).Rakesh.Koteshwara Rao. Mukesh Rishi(Dharmendra Reddy).Srinivas Rudra.Sanjay. Bitthiri Sathi(Self).Bhavani Shankar.Shekar. Thakur Anoop Singh(Aadhi).Sivannarayana. Apoorva Srinivasan(Lakshmi).Suresh.Bangalore Suresh.Silver Suresh.Surya. Hari Teja(Hariteja).Twinkle. Prithvi Vazir((as Prithvi)).Venu.Vijay

Language Telugu.

Producers Madhu B.. Julia Maksimenko. Anna Palenchuk. Nallamalupu Sreenivas.

Production Light House Movie Makers. Sri Lakshmi Narasimha Productions.
